{"tid":2182800,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"市民旺角聚集悼念8.31 樓上髮廊舉鏡警即舉槍","createTime":"2020-08-31T14:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T15:23:45.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c87736c54ee5c7074471d6549ed3da84a2232e69","tid":2182800,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:02:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/SUST73Y74RDJPFM4J6O743IB44/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FSUST73Y74RDJPFM4J6O743IB44%2F&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr02rU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=567d620d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200831%2FSUST73Y74RDJPFM4J6O743IB44%2F&h=bde285d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200831/SUST73Y74RDJPFM4J6O743IB44/</a><br />\n<br />\n下午9時25分左右，到旺角增援的警員在西洋菜南街及亞皆老街馬路中心舉起藍旗，其後沿西洋菜南街往油麻地方向推進，其間有樓上髮廊從窗邊舉起幾面鏡，警員即大為緊張，舉起胡椒球彈槍及電筒，並要求記者拍攝「鏡人」。9時30分，大批防暴警沿西洋菜南街推進至旺角中心一帶，在快富街追截多名市民進行搜查，共有約30名市民分別在快富街7-11和卓悅外被截查，當中有市民手持白色鮮花。"},{"pid":"1a5e3eba721213f9ef445cb9bf635c5ff83a0d69","tid":2182800,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"今日有無過千GREEN OBJECT呃糧"},{"pid":"2c7298ad02e631b418d90a472dc2d988624040de","tid":2182800,"uid":200083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:05:34.000Z","msg":"仲叫記者做野 咩年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cfd9575f006ac533577769fefd261bc7827c52","tid":2182800,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a5e3eba721213f9ef445cb9bf635c5ff83a0d69","tid":2182800,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"今日有無過千GREEN OBJECT呃糧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:09:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" c